

                        E-Commerce Website

                    Front End : Using Angular 

    1.create angular project - ng new project-name 
    2.Run angular project - ng s -o 
    3.add boostrap, font awesome, google fonts in index.html 
    4.Clean code app component.html 
    5.create lazyloading module - for all all-products
        ng g m module-name --route module-name --module rootModule
    6.create component 
        - header - appModule
        - all-products - lazy loading  - productsModule
        - cart - productsModule
        - wishlist - productsModule
        - footer - appModule
        - page-not-found -appModule
        - view product - productsModule 
    7.set up the path for each components 
        -all-products 
        -cart 
        -wishlist 
        -view product
    8.design component 
    9.create Services - to make api call
    
